descriptionMarkdown:
This is a simple early-game small electric pole producer.

INPUTS:
* Bottom-left: Raw wood
* Bottom-right: Copper plate

OUTPUTS:
* Middle-right: Small electric pole

Other properties:
* Horizontally and vertically tileable

Changelog:
 * Revision 2: Reduced small electric pole requirement by position adjustments
 * Revision 1: Initial Release

When tiling vertically, you can align as follows for more compactness (image is based on an older version):

![Recommended vertical alignment](https://i.imgur.com/9pzx54n.png)

This blueprint was designed with extreme simplicity in mind. You can even build just the bottom half to get basic production going, if you don't want to deal with underground belt production yet.
title: Early Game Small Electric Pole
